description: The dirty dozen refers to the fruits and vegetables that are the most contaminated by pesticide use. Use this skill to learn which fruits and vegetables are on the dirty dozen list. You can try phrases like: "Alexa, ask Dirty Dozen, what fruits are in the dirty dozen list?" or "Alexa, ask Dirty Dozen, how dirty are cherry tomatoes?" or "Alexa, ask Dirty Dozen, how clean are strawberries?"
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Dirty Dozen what fruits are in the dirty dozen list?
Alexa ask Dirty Dozen how dirty are cherry tomatoes?
name: Dirty Dozen (Vegetables and Fruits)
shortDescription: Learn which fruits and vegetables are on the dirty dozen list and pesticide contaminated.
